headline: Wall Street Loves Williams-Sonoma Right Now—Here’s Why the Stock Could Soar in 2026
summary: Williams-Sonoma reported strong Q3 earnings with rising margins and share repurchases, driving bullish analyst forecasts and solidifying its long-term value.
